<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>织影 StitchEcho — 下载</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, "PingFang SC", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FAF5F5 0%, #F0E8EA 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    }
    .card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 48px 32px;
      max-width: 400px;
      width: 90%;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(61,43,46,0.08);
    }
    .icon { font-size: 64px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .title { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: #2D1E20; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .sub { font-size: 14px; color: #A08A90; margin-bottom: 32px; line-height: 1.6; }
    .download-btn {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 16px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C9969F, #A07078);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .download-btn:active { opacity: 0.85; }
    .web-link {
      display: block;
      padding: 14px;
      border: 1px solid #EAD8DA;
      border-radius: 14px;
      color: #C9969F;
      font-size: 15px;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .info {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #A08A90;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .info a { color: #C9969F; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="icon">🧶</div>
    <div class="title">织影 StitchEcho</div>
    <div class="sub">钩织针法追踪 · 离线可用 · 数据本地存储</div>

    <a class="download-btn" href="app-debug.apk" download>下载 Android APK</a>
    <a class="web-link" href="web/">打开网页版</a>

    <div class="info">
      安装前请允许「未知来源」应用安装<br>
      反馈与建议：<a href="https://github.com/isabellelau/StitchEcho-down">GitHub</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
